description:
The time has come to say goodbye to Hermitcraft Season 10. In this episode, procrastinator Etho goes into full panic mode as he madly races to finish whatever projects and ideas he can before the time runs out.

We focus on finishing the upstairs of our base, connect Gem and my base together with a proper sewer system, give our animals a home in a new stable, and tidying up the terraforming and rough patches around our area.

We check out our best run of Metro Mayhem Season 2. Then we are joined by the brilliant BdoubleO as we embark through Tango's Tangler; 4 grueling puzzles to test our perfect teamwork and communication skills.

Thank you for joining us throughout this wonderful season!
